                                    <h2 class="mt-20 mb-20">No gutters <a href="" id="No-gutters"
                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                    <p>With <code>.g-0</code>, users can get rid of the gutters between the columns in our predefined grid classes. This gets rid of the negative margins in <code>.row</code> and the horizontal padding in any columns that are its immediate descendants.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>Need edge-to-edge design? To avoid overflow, remove the parent <code>.container</code> or <code>.container-fluid</code> and add <code>.mx-0</code> to the <code>.row</code>.
                                    </p>
